graph TB
    subgraph "Training Operator Deployment"
        Manager[training-operator manager<br/>Go binary]

        subgraph "Controllers"
            PyTorchCtrl[PyTorchJob Controller<br/>Elastic support]
            TFCtrl[TFJob Controller]
            MPICtrl[MPIJob Controller]
            XGBoostCtrl[XGBoostJob Controller]
            MXCtrl[MXJob Controller]
            PaddleCtrl[PaddleJob Controller]
        end

        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Metrics[Metrics Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        Health[Health Probe Server<br/>8081/TCP HTTP]

        Manager -->|manages| PyTorchCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| TFCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| MPICtrl
        Manager -->|manages| XGBoostCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| MXCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| PaddleCtrl
        Manager -->|serves| Webhook
        Manager -->|exposes| Metrics
        Manager -->|exposes| Health
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        PyTorchJob[PyTorchJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        TFJob[TFJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        MPIJob[MPIJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        XGBoostJob[XGBoostJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        MXJob[MXJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        PaddleJob[PaddleJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources"
        Pods[Training Pods]
        Services[Pod Services]
        ConfigMaps[ConfigMaps]
        RoleBindings[RoleBindings]
        HPA[HorizontalPodAutoscaler<br/>PyTorch Elastic]
        PodGroup[PodGroup<br/>Gang Scheduling]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| PyTorchJob
    User -->|creates| TFJob
    User -->|creates| MPIJob

    PyTorchJob -->|watched by| PyTorchCtrl
    TFJob -->|watched by| TFCtrl
    MPIJob -->|watched by| MPICtrl
    XGBoostJob -->|watched by| XGBoostCtrl
    MXJob -->|watched by| MXCtrl
    PaddleJob -->|watched by| PaddleCtrl

    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| Pods
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| Services
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| ConfigMaps
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| HPA
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| PodGroup

    TFCtrl -->|creates| Pods
    MPICtrl -->|creates| Pods

    Webhook -->|validates/mutates| PyTorchJob
    Webhook -->|validates/mutates| TFJob
    Webhook -->|validates/mutates| MPIJob

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Volcano[Volcano Scheduler<br/>Optional]
        SchedulerPlugins[Scheduler-Plugins<br/>Optional]
        Prometheus[Prometheus]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Webhook certs]
    end

    Manager -->|reconciles via| K8sAPI
    PodGroup -.->|used by| Volcano
    PodGroup -.->|used by| SchedulerPlugins
    Metrics -->|scraped by| Prometheus
    Webhook -->|certs from| CertManager

    subgraph "Internal ODH Integration"
        ModelController[odh-model-controller<br/>Model serving]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>Sidecar disabled]
    end

    Pods -.->|produces models for| ModelController
    Manager -.->|network policy| ServiceMesh

